name: When the Gateway of India gets trapped!
description: This image shows one of the greatest monuments of India with a different perspective. It was captured using two devices and composed/graded on Adobe Photoshop and Lightroom. It gained good popularity when I first released it on Instagram, it got many re-shares and it also won the Photoshop competition on World Photographers Club and was chosen to be the photo of the day on 5th December, 2018.  Artist - Sagar Narula Instagram - @sagar_narula Twitter - @sagarnarulaa Location - Mumbai, India
